Class LND10Function

java.lang.Object
  tests.LND10Function
All Implemented Interfaces:
FunctionIntf
public class LND10Function
extends java.lang.Object
implements FunctionIntf

class implements the so-called LND10 function (continuous, non-differentiable). Its global minimum value is always zero. The function is called "Chained crescent II". See Haarala (2004) and Brimberg et al (2013).

Title: popt4jlib

Description: A Parallel Meta-Heuristic Optimization Library in Java
